#: ../../../topics/benchmarking.rst:54
msgid ""
"That tells you that Scrapy is able to crawl about 3900 pages per minute in "
"the hardware where you run it. Note that this is a very simple spider "
"intended to follow links, any custom spider you write will probably do more "
"stuff which results in slower crawl rates. How slower depends on how much "
"your spider does and how well it's written."
msgstr ""

